{"tid":2355693,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 突 發 ］小妹終於搵到間值得推介嘅燒肉黃店","createTime":"2021-01-06T09:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T05:35:05.000Z","uid":13361,"like":148,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c221af07553a64678cadbace6cc09d388ad3141c","tid":2355693,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQisOME.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQisOME.png&h=57003c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九宮格牛肉 咩都有 A4和牛都有 兩個人分岩岩好 原價$288 由於新開張午市七折 但加一無折 所以折實係$230 七折後好抵食！btw由於小妹影得太樣衰所以呢張圖係openrice偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九宮格有啲咩可以睇以下張圖 小妹都分唔晒邊樣打邊樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M14DaZZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM14DaZZ.png&h=688e2378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jNUtNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jNUtNQ.jpg&h=0fccfd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於九宮格有厚切牛舌了 所以點咗碟薄切牛舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大概有三十塊 折後只需要五十幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁多塊牛舌 食得好過癮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5eLArG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5eLArG.jpg&h=3930a073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞腎好爽口唔un <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燒芝士年糕不嬲都正 佢仲要配埋煉奶 不過自己燒有啲難燒 菠蘿有啲酸 雞軟骨正常<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMVF8MJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMVF8MJ.jpg&h=a501e61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味噌黑豚五花 調味唔錯 想食豬可以叫呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzgqArL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzgqArL.jpg&h=8e7cd348&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMXdKj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMXdKj6.jpg&h=16723857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後個<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">燒飯團勁正</span></span>！燒到每一面都脆卜卜 再塗滿勁大兜嘅明太子醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好味到哭𠹌左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食唔返點算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />折實只係$16 仲抵過日本7仔啲飯糰 仲要有滿滿嘅明太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔食飯糰仲有啲類似牛角飯嘅飯嗌<br />\n<br />\n埋單只係四百零蚊 肉就一定夠多 如果想食飽啲可以叫多幾個飯糰或者牛角飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平日下午茶時間都差唔多full晒 記得去佢Facebook book枱 用餐時間90分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環境：座位闊落  枱與枱之間分隔得開 係個爐gas味有啲重 <br />\n總結：七折好抵食呀！但如果無七折嘅話就會慳啲嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能剩係食牛舌 飯糰 加豬肉<br />\nQr code落單好方便 上菜又快 兩個人一定唔會燒唔晒  <br />\nBtw 老細可唔可以長期午市都有七折呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n名：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e727ec17e01eb433b9c42db15aab39a61b43d31","tid":2355693,"uid":160963,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"有棍小妹"},{"pid":"8f5a48ada4be2e00cfb23c4468c4026633e8bf4d","tid":2355693,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f1351b37288c9d8063dbe71f2ed4234c55a90d90","tid":2355693,"uid":250291,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"【2021首個行動post】全民文宣連儂日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=dbd6af39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&h=2eee38b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/135760301_2741317849516339_41508721484844777_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=WjLqJBXQcqUAX_tLILU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.xx&amp;oh=fb638f3c6308a3eb2b313b82b59d520b&amp;oe=601C7DDA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F135760301_2741317849516339_41508721484844777_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3DWjLqJBXQcqUAX_tLILU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-2.xx%26oh%3Dfb638f3c6308a3eb2b313b82b59d520b%26oe%3D601C7DDA&h=3f6a81b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/136684605_2741317896183001_8531677324604596330_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=d9g0bNygB_0AX8B4SeH&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.xx&amp;oh=a27fe705576225eb6df9a42f188ac677&amp;oe=601B6C6D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F136684605_2741317896183001_8531677324604596330_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3Dd9g0bNygB_0AX8B4SeH%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-2.xx%26oh%3Da27fe705576225eb6df9a42f188ac677%26oe%3D601B6C6D&h=b64d87f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/136639341_2741317929516331_1099685243406799757_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=ESmQ7mI_jGwAX_ZEkFh&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.xx&amp;oh=356af3cfef1b1500d977554245f89cd5&amp;oe=601A92AB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F136639341_2741317929516331_1099685243406799757_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3DESmQ7mI_jGwAX_ZEkFh%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-1.xx%26oh%3D356af3cfef1b1500d977554245f89cd5%26oe%3D601A92AB&h=bc15e78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明未來到，先有大抓捕。<br />\n抗爭平靜片刻，港共立即反噬。<br />\n港共就係要我地恐懼。<br />\n要我地放棄。<br />\n要我地徒勞。<br />\n<br />\n唯獨抗爭意志不滅。<br />\n8/1-11/1，星光燎原，遍地開花！<br />\n寧鳴而死，不默而生！"},{"pid":"902e8f3e3dc419f71752adb89c7ab710a10df6a3","tid":2355693,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2e727ec17e01eb433b9c42db15aab39a61b43d31","tid":2355693,"uid":160963,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"有棍小妹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"巨棍小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca5d5f9ab16c45948b1bc100de8d2b094222fc6","tid":2355693,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee2fac737f48cff7d7245c3b8e8bb91dd69247d","tid":2355693,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"尖咀<br />\n驚安<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f188346e62f2150a17e123d357c947655a75be76","tid":2355693,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"最憎食咁多款牛牌仔都冇個"},{"pid":"1b56efebc80f6b22c84f9289d530432994bcbcdc","tid":2355693,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"f188346e62f2150a17e123d357c947655a75be76","tid":2355693,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"最憎食咁多款牛牌仔都冇個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"又唔係啲咩高級嘢 無所謂啦