 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔食飯糰仲有啲類似牛角飯嘅飯嗌<br />\n<br />\n埋單只係四百零蚊 肉就一定夠多 如果想食飽啲可以叫多幾個飯糰或者牛角飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平日下午茶時間都差唔多full晒 記得去佢Facebook book枱 用餐時間90分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環境：座位闊落  枱與枱之間分隔得開 係個爐gas味有啲重 <br />\n總結：七折好抵食呀！但如果無七折嘅話就會慳啲嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能剩係食牛舌 飯糰 加豬肉<br />\nQr code落單好方便 上菜又快 兩個人一定唔會燒唔晒  <br />\nBtw 老細可唔可以長期午市都有七折呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n名：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"小妹 有巨龍定小龍 小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4c096e3847bd1aa5688d1737f07244c744869f","tid":2355693,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a959fa458e3f7d9a1ac6b1a4fba5d7cea2050c1","tid":2355693,"uid":66945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢係咪請好多人幫佢賣廣告???我見ig又有,fb page又有....<br />\n成日覺得搵人賣廣告都係伏中之伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過上星期六食左,又真係ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"係 好多廣告"},{"pid":"4296b43a5cee6ea24f78c072c6722cf5b20e52ac","tid":2355693,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"567c23ff3cf6ead6e3ebb090c137f6a2ef024b11","tid":2355693,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"職員會唔會幫手燒/教點燒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係貴嘢黎架"},{"pid":"d1e5018fd5dc3876d9eeb18b98d71e28e8fd051d","tid":2355693,"uid":13361,"like":0